Hello, thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, the finest bowling alley experience in town! My name is Alex. May I know your name, please?

Hi Alex, my name is Jamie.

Thank you, Jamie. How can I assist you with your billing inquiry today?

I received a bill in the mail, but I'm not sure what it's for. Can you help me understand it?

Of course, Jamie. To better assist you, could you please verify the billing statement number for me? It should be a combination of letters and numbers.

Sure, the statement number is W-B-H-H-zero one two three four.

Thank you. And could you also provide the last four digits of the phone number associated with your account?

Yes, it's five six seven eight.

Thank you, Jamie. I see the billing is for the recent tournament registration and lane bookings. I hope that clarifies everything.

Yes, it does. Thank you for explaining that.

You're welcome, Jamie. If you have any more questions, feel free to call us anytime. Thank you for choosing West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
